Description: Stretching beyond the horizon, the Radiant Plains are bathed in eternal sunlight. Fields of luminescent flowers sway gently in the breeze, each petal glowing with its own inner light. Crystal-clear streams cross the landscape, their waters shimmering like liquid silver. At night, the plains transform as bioluminescent plants and insects illuminate the darkness, mirroring the starry sky above. The atmosphere is serene and uplifting, a haven for the Light beasts that embody purity and brilliance.